<div class="content-card">
    <h2>Welcome!</h2>

    <p>
        Pickleball is my favorite hobby because it’s easy to learn, competitive, and social.
        You can play casually with friends or take it seriously and improve your strategy and consistency.
    </p>

    <p>
        I like that pickleball combines quick reactions with smart shot placement. The game rewards good footwork,
        controlled shots at the net, and knowing when to slow the point down versus when to attack.
    </p>

    <p>
        My favorite skills to practice are serving with consistency, dinking at the kitchen line, and resetting the ball
        when I get pulled out of position. It’s fun because even small improvements show up quickly in real games.
    </p>

