        <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618329027137-0a7d0f8e3b59?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=60"
            alt="Pickleball court" />
    </div>

    <p class="note">
        Want help improving? Use the tutoring calculator to estimate lesson cost:
        <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Calculator">Go to the calculator</a>.
    </p>
